      • checkIn

        public MotelRoom checkIn​(RoachColony colony,
                         java.lang.String roomType,
                         java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.String> amenities)
        If the RoachMotel is vacant, checks the argument RoachColony in to a MotelRoom indicated by the argument String, decorated with the Amenities indicated by the ArrayList of Strings. If the MotelRoom is not vacant, adds the RoachColony to a waitlist to be notified when the RoachMotel is vacant.
        Parameters:
        colony - the RoachColony attempting to check in
        roomType - the type of room the RoachColony is attempting to check into (Regular, Deluxe, Suite)
        amenities - the type of amenities wanted with the room (FoodBar, RefillBar, Shower, Spa)
        Returns:
        the MotelRoom that the RoachColony is checked into, or a vacant room if the RoachMotel is not vacant
